pull_request.title: guard external testing against algorithm absence
pull_request.body: This PR introduces a check for algorithm presence to avoid recurrence of [CI failures](https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/open-quantum-safe/oqs-provider/1159/workflows/0e82312f-a472-492a-943d-16dbb5450a03/jobs/4859) due to bad `liboqs` configuration(s).

pull_request.title: Small fixes after adding ML-*
pull_request.body:
Two small fixes after #1626:
- The fragment to filter "STD" signature algorithms contained an error
- The script to reproduce ML-* vectors used an incorrect directory name
